 koje poštuju

502
00:17:01,860 --> 00:17:02,560
 ta prava

503
00:17:02,560 --> 00:17:04,660
 i koje ne poštuju.

504
00:17:04,660 --> 00:17:05,400
 I vidimo

505
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:07,620
 odakle ljudi bježe

506
00:17:07,620 --> 00:17:08,500
 odakle ne bježe.

507
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:08,860
 Dakle,

508
00:17:08,860 --> 00:17:09,600
 to je prilično

509
00:17:09,600 --> 00:17:11,380
 neumoljiva stvarnost

510
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:12,280
 i na neki način

511
00:17:12,280 --> 00:17:13,700
 je empiriska.

512
00:17:13,700 --> 00:17:13,960
 Odnosno,

513
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:14,660
 ne na neki način

514
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:15,420
 svakako je

515
00:17:15,420 --> 00:17:16,500
 empiriska.

516
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:16,820
 Dakle,

517
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:18,400
 to je u startu

518
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,060
 jedna vjera.

519
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:20,640
 Ona nije

520
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:23,400
 uobičajena vjera,

521
00:17:23,400 --> 00:17:24,020
 kako kažemo,

522
00:17:24,020 --> 00:17:25,140
 religiozna vjera,

523
00:17:25,140 --> 00:17:26,260
 ali je nekak vrsta

524
00:17:26,260 --> 00:17:27,760
 građanske sekularne vjere.

525
00:17:27,760 --> 00:17:29,580
 Poklanjamo

526
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:30,220
 povjerenje

527
00:17:30,220 --> 00:17:31,140
 tim svojim

528
00:17:31,140 --> 00:17:33,400
 umskim

529
00:17:33,400 --> 00:17:34,580
 dosezima

530
00:17:34,580 --> 00:17:35,340
 i zaključcima.

531
00:17:35,340 --> 00:17:37,800
 Naravno,

532
00:17:37,800 --> 00:17:38,080
 mi,

533
00:17:38,080 --> 00:17:39,680
 konkretno kršćani,

534
00:17:39,680 --> 00:17:40,980
 utemeljujemo,

535
00:17:40,980 --> 00:17:42,460
 to je i Maritain činio,

536
00:17:42,460 --> 00:17:43,280
 te ideje

537
00:17:43,280 --> 00:17:44,380
 na dubljoj razini,

538
00:17:44,380 --> 00:17:45,600
 ali oni su

539
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:46,880
 očito prihvatljivi

540
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:47,780
 ljudima koji ne

541
00:17:47,780 --> 00:17:49,120
 prihvaćaju

542
00:17:49,120 --> 00:17:49,940
 tu dublju razinu.

543
00:17:49,940 --> 00:17:51,020
 Iz nekog razloga su im

544
00:17:51,020 --> 00:17:51,700
 ipak prihvatljivi

545
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:53,060
 zato jer su kompatibilni

546
00:17:53,060 --> 00:17:55,200
 sa racijom

547
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,100
 i sa savješću.

548
00:17:56,240 --> 00:17:57,280
 opet nikako ne možemo

549
00:17:57,280 --> 00:17:57,980
 povijeti od vjere.

550
00:17:57,980 --> 00:17:58,620
 Samo je pitanje

551
00:17:58,620 --> 00:17:59,720
 u šta ćemo je temeljiti.

552
00:17:59,720 --> 00:18:00,380
 Ali evo,

553
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:01,400
 sad je nedavno bio

554
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:02,140
 jedan slučaj

555
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:03,520
 presuda suda

556
00:18:03,520 --> 00:18:04,140
 Europske unije

557
00:18:04,140 --> 00:18:04,700
 koji je čini mi se

558
00:18:04,700 --> 00:18:06,160
 prošao dosta

559
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:06,760
 ispod radara.

560
00:18:06,760 --> 00:18:07,320
 Meni se čini

561
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:08,420
 prilično znakovitim

562
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:09,420
 upravo u ovom kontekstu.

563
00:18:09,420 --> 00:18:10,080
 Znači,

564
00:18:10,080 --> 00:18:11,700
 bile je presuđeno

565
00:18:11,700 --> 00:18:12,160
 oko toga

566
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:13,640
 da li kompanija

567
00:18:13,640 --> 00:18:13,960
 smije

568
00:18:13,960 --> 00:18:15,140
 zabraniti ženama

569
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:15,580
 pravo

570
00:18:15,580 --> 00:18:16,340
 da nose hijab.

571
00:18:16,980 --> 00:18:18,360
 i odluka suda

572
00:18:18,360 --> 00:18:18,940
 Europske unije

573
00:18:18,940 --> 00:18:19,660
 bilo da smije

574
00:18:19,660 --> 00:18:20,920
 uz obrazloženje

575
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:22,100
 interno pravilo tvrtke

576
00:18:22,100 --> 00:18:23,080
 koje zabranjuje

577
00:18:23,080 --> 00:18:23,920
 vidljivo onošenje

578
00:18:23,920 --> 00:18:25,100
 vjerskih, filozofskih

579
00:18:25,100 --> 00:18:26,140
 ili duhovnih znakova

580
00:18:26,140 --> 00:18:27,300
 ne predstavlja

581
00:18:27,300 --> 00:18:28,460
 izravnu diskriminaciju

582
00:18:28,460 --> 00:18:29,320
 ako se primjenjuje

583
00:18:29,320 --> 00:18:30,100
 na sve radnike,

584
00:18:30,100 --> 00:18:30,740
 naopćenit

585
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:32,660
 i ne diferencira način.

586
00:18:32,660 --> 00:18:33,540
 Sad,

587
00:18:33,540 --> 00:18:34,260
 meni se čini

588
00:18:34,260 --> 00:18:35,020
 da je ovo zapravo

589
00:18:35,020 --> 00:18:35,760
 otvaranje vrata

590
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:36,340
 da će sutra

591
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:37,040
 netko ko dođe

592
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:37,780
 sa križem

593
00:18:37,780 --> 00:18:39,200
 prema ovoj odluci

594
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,040
 suda Europske unije

595
00:18:40,040 --> 00:18:40,920
 da će mu poslodavac

596
00:18:40,920 --> 00:18:41,780
 možeš ećo prosti

597
00:18:41,780 --> 00:18:42,360
 ali skrižem

598
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:43,500
 ne možeš u našu kompaniju

599
00:18:43,500 --> 00:18:44,240
 i nitko drugi

600
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,500
 ne može niti skrižem

601
00:18:45,500 --> 00:18:46,660
 niti sa hijabom

602
00:18:46,660 --> 00:18:47,240
 ili bilo kojim

603
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,220
 drugim vjerskim obilježem

604
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:49,200
 u kompaniju.

605
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:49,940
 Meni se to čini

606
00:18:49,940 --> 00:18:51,280
 prilično diskriminirajući.

607
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:55,980
 Prethodna napomena

608
00:18:55,980 --> 00:18:56,360
 samo,

609
00:18:56,360 --> 00:18:57,100
 to su isto ovako

610
00:18:57,100 --> 00:18:58,060
 neke trivialne stvari

611
00:18:58,060 --> 00:18:59,020
 ali ja ih volim uvijek

612
00:18:59,020 --> 00:18:59,920
 ponovno i ponovno

613
00:18:59,920 --> 00:19:00,380
 navoditi.

614
00:19:00,380 --> 00:19:01,580
 Diskriminacija

615
00:19:01,580 --> 00:19:02,360
 sama po sebi

616
00:19:02,360 --> 00:19:03,520
 je neizbježna.

617
00:19:03,520 --> 00:19:04,020
 Dakle,

618
00:19:04,020 --> 00:19:05,880
 diskriminirati etimološki

619
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:06,380
 u nekom smislu

620
00:19:06,380 --> 00:19:07,780
 znači razlikovati,

621
00:19:07,860 --> 00:19:08,540
 razlučivati,

622
00:19:08,540 --> 00:19:09,160
 lučiti.

623
00:19:09,160 --> 00:19:10,840
 Mi ne možemo

624
00:19:10,840 --> 00:19:11,740
 ne diskriminirati.

625
00:19:11,740 --> 00:19:12,680
 Mi diskriminiramo

626
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,640
 džake po znanju.

627
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:15,420
 Ko zna više dobije pet,

628
00:19:15,420 --> 00:19:16,540
 ko zna manje dobije tri.

629
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:17,280
 Dakle,

630
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:18,180
 to je diskriminacija,

631
00:19:18,180 --> 00:19:21,060
 ali pravedna diskriminacija.

632
00:19:21,060 --> 00:19:21,420
 Dakle,

633
00:19:21,420 --> 00:19:22,100
 mi razlikujemo

634
00:19:22,100 --> 00:19:23,560
 diskriminaciju koja je pravedna

635
00:19:23,560 --> 00:19:25,300
 i diskriminaciju koja je nepravedna.

636
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:26,040
 Dakle,

637
00:19:26,040 --> 00:19:26,880
 ovdje bi trebalo govoriti

638
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,420
 radili se o nepravednoj diskriminaciji.

639
00:19:28,420 --> 00:19:29,420
 Ja ću ovako reći,

640
00:19:29,420 --> 00:19:32,520
 iako znam za taj slučaj

641
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:34,600
 i ne mogu ga valorizirati

642
00:19:34,600 --> 00:19:36,020
 sa specifično neke

643
00:19:36,020 --> 00:19:38,960
 juridičke pozicije.

644
00:19:38,960 --> 00:19:40,780
 Nisam u tom smislu ekspert.

645
00:19:40,780 --> 00:19:42,960
 Ali ću se ipak usuditi reći

646
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:45,760
 da je u nekom smislu

647
00:19:45,760 --> 00:19:47,020
 uvreda zdravom razumu.

648
00:19:47,020 --> 00:19:48,400
 Uvreda zdravom razumu.

649
00:19:48,400 --> 00:19:48,800
 Dakle,

650
00:19:48,800 --> 00:19:52,140
 ne vidim zaista nikakvog razloga

651
00:19:52,140 --> 00:19:53,900
 da bi se nekoj ženi

652
00:19:53,900 --> 00:19:54,920
 zabranjivao

653
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,880
 hijab.

654
00:19:58,380 --> 00:19:59,560
 S druge strane,

655
00:19:59,560 --> 00:20:00,720
 ovo tvoje pitanje

656
00:20:00,720 --> 00:20:01,640
 ili strepnja

657
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,380
 da se time otvara u vrata,

658
00:20:03,380 --> 00:20:03,600
 da,

659
00:20:03,600 --> 00:20:05,060
 ta strepnja je tu

660
00:20:05,060 --> 00:20:06,820
 i to ne bi bilo prvi put u povijesti.

661
00:20:06,820 --> 00:20:07,100
 Dakle,

662
00:20:07,100 --> 00:20:08,740
 ona cijelo vrijeme visi

663
00:20:08,740 --> 00:20:10,000
 nad nama.

664
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:10,720
 Dakle,

665
00:20:10,720 --> 00:20:12,460
 to je moguće da se dogodi,

666
00:20:12,460 --> 00:20:14,020
 nije uopće nezamislivo.

667
00:20:14,020 --> 00:20:15,880
 U nekom smislu se i događa.

668
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:16,380
 Dakle,

669
00:20:16,380 --> 00:20:18,120
 taj progon religijskoga je

670
00:20:18,120 --> 00:20:18,940
 neki kontinuum.

671
00:20:18,940 --> 00:20:19,380
 Dakle,

672
00:20:19,380 --> 00:20:19,940
 mi to gledamo.

673
00:20:19,940 --> 00:20:20,920
 Ne samo kršćanstva,

674
00:20:20,920 --> 00:20:22,580
 ali kršćanstva najviše.

675
00:20:22,580 --> 00:20:24,320
 Ne treba se to zvuči

676
00:20:24,320 --> 00:20:25,760
 pristrano i neskromno,

677
00:20:25,760 --> 00:20:27,000
 ali kršćanstva najviše.

678
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,260
 I danas je statistički

679
00:20:28,260 --> 00:20:29,940
 kršćanstvo ili kršćani

680
00:20:29,940 --> 00:20:30,700
 na svjetskoj razini

681
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:31,520
 najprogonjenija

682
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:32,620
 religijska skupina.

683
00:20:32,620 --> 00:20:34,460
 Međutim,

684
00:20:34,460 --> 00:20:35,880
 ovdje stajemo na stranu

685
00:20:35,880 --> 00:20:37,680
 dotične žene

686
00:20:37,680 --> 00:20:39,480
 i ja zaista ne vidim

687
00:20:39,480 --> 00:20:40,440
 nikakvog razloga

688
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,140
 zašto bi se

689
00:20:41,140 --> 00:20:43,140
 hijab zabranjivao.

690
00:20:43,140 --> 00:20:44,380
 U krajnjoj liniji

691
00:20:44,380 --> 00:20:45,360
 mi imamo nešto slično

692
00:20:45,360 --> 00:20:46,320
 i kod naših častih

693
00:20:46,320 --> 00:20:47,640
 se stara nekakvu vrstu

694
00:20:47,640 --> 00:20:48,580
 pokrivanja glave.

695
00:20:48,580 --> 00:20:53,560
 S druge strane,

696
00:20:53,560 --> 00:20:55,040
 treba biti iskreni reći

697
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,900
 da nije isti problem

698
00:20:56,900 --> 00:20:57,560
 sa, recimo,

699
00:20:57,560 --> 00:20:58,180
 Nikabom

700
00:20:58,180 --> 00:20:59,280
 ili Burkom.

701
00:20:59,280 --> 00:21:00,540
 Dakle,

702
00:21:00,540 --> 00:21:01,860
 mogu otvoren reći,

703
00:21:01,860 --> 00:21:02,840
 ja sam tu razgovarao

704
00:21:02,840 --> 00:21:03,980
 i sa našim domaćim,

705
00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:04,620
 da tako kažem,

706
00:21:04,620 --> 00:21:05,240
 zagrebačkim

707
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:06,100
 ili sarajevskim

708
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:07,880
 muslimanima.

709
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:10,380
 To nije sasvim isto.

710
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:10,860
 Ne znam,

711
00:21:10,860 --> 00:21:11,500
 možemo li mi

712
00:21:11,500 --> 00:21:12,720
 u evropskom kontekstu

713
00:21:12,720 --> 00:21:14,480
 pristati dugoročno

714
00:21:14,480 --> 00:21:16,300
 na kompletno pokrivanje

715
00:21:16,300 --> 00:21:17,380
 lica u javnosti.

716
00:21:17,380 --> 00:21:18,620
 U krajnjoj liniji

717
00:21:18,620 --> 00:21:20,600
 sa nekakvog sigurnosnog aspekta.

718
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:22,320
 To nije odgovor

719
00:21:22,320 --> 00:21:23,440
 koji ja mogu ponuditi

720
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:24,480
 gotov na stol.

721
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:24,760
 Dakle,

722
00:21:24,760 --> 00:21:26,480
 nema matematičkog,

723
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:27,600
 geometrijskog odgovora

724
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,260
 na to pitanje.

725
00:21:28,260 --> 00:21:30,060
 I to je određena vrsta

726
00:21:30,060 --> 00:21:31,080
 problema.

727
00:21:31,080 --> 00:21:31,440
 Dakle,

728
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,300
 kad je riječ o

729
00:21:32,300 --> 00:21:34,380
 kompletnom pokrivanju lica,

730
00:21:34,380 --> 00:21:35,680
 to je potpuno,

731
00:21:35,680 --> 00:21:36,260
 po meni,

732
00:21:36,260 --> 00:21:36,960
 neusporedivo

733
00:21:36,960 --> 00:21:37,300
 sa hijabom.

734
00:21:37,300 --> 00:21:38,280
 Dakle,

735
00:21:38,280 --> 00:21:38,860
 gdje je lice

736
00:21:38,860 --> 00:21:40,080
 jasno vidljivo.

737
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:42,580
 meni se više čini da se tu radi

738
00:21:42,580 --> 00:21:45,420
 o sekularizmu

739
00:21:45,420 --> 00:21:47,380
 u onoj njegovoj negativnoj

740
00:21:47,380 --> 00:21:47,940
 varijanti,

741
00:21:47,940 --> 00:21:49,820
 sa negativnom konotacijom,

742
00:21:49,820 --> 00:21:52,140
 kojem smeta nešto

743
00:21:52,140 --> 00:21:53,420
 samo zato što je religijsko.

744
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:56,400
 i tu se po meni radi

745
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:57,900
 o pogrešnoj odluci suda.

746
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:58,480
 Naravno,

747
00:21:58,480 --> 00:21:59,120
 netko će pitati

748
00:21:59,120 --> 00:21:59,780
 ko si ti

749
00:21:59,780 --> 00:22:02,360
 da prosuđuješ odluke suda.

750
00:22:02,360 --> 00:22:03,320
 Moj odgovor je da nisam

751
00:22:03,320 --> 00:22:03,600
 niko,

752
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,620
 niko ni ništa posebno,

753
00:22:05,620 --> 00:22:06,840
 ali svojedno

754
00:22:06,840 --> 00:22:08,320
 donosim sude

755
00:22:08,320 --> 00:22:09,320
 da je odluka

756
00:22:09,320 --> 00:22:09,960
 promašena

757
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,420
 i da treba biti

758
00:22:11,420 --> 00:22:12,180
 jako oprezan

759
00:22:12,180 --> 00:22:12,940
 na to.

760
00:22:12,940 --> 00:22:13,900
 U krajnjoj liniji

761
00:22:13,900 --> 00:22:14,880
 u tim dilemama

762
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:17,480
 između

763
00:22:17,480 --> 00:22:19,640
 slobode savjesti

764
00:22:19,640 --> 00:22:21,920
 i konkretno vjeroispovijesti

765
00:22:21,920 --> 00:22:25,340
 i državnog propisivanja.

766
00:22:25,340 --> 00:22:28,160
 Mi,

767
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:30,260
 premda ne možemo davati

768
00:22:30,260 --> 00:22:31,080
 geometrijske,

769
00:22:31,080 --> 00:22:32,120
 matematički,

770
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:32,640
 kiruški,

771
00:22:32,640 --> 00:22:33,700
 precizne odgovore,

772
00:22:33,700 --> 00:22:35,760
 jer postoje neke dileme

773
00:22:35,760 --> 00:22:36,420
 će nas dovesti

774
00:22:36,420 --> 00:22:37,580
 ono pred aporije,

775
00:22:37,580 --> 00:22:38,100
 ono jednostavno

776
00:22:38,100 --> 00:22:38,840
 nećemo znat

777
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:39,580
 što sad.

778
00:22:39,580 --> 00:22:41,060
 Ono što možemo

779
00:22:41,060 --> 00:22:41,800
 ipak ustanoviti

780
00:22:41,800 --> 00:22:42,400
 kao načelo

781
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:43,080
 to je da

782
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:44,880
 uvijek

